Well…. we’re growin’ fam. We’ll be adding one more to the family coming this summer! We’ve been so excited to share this news with you and can’t wait to start this journey together. We feel so blessed to be in this position right now and are thrilled to get to do this a second time! Make sure to subscribe & follow with us throughout this pregnancy.. Here we go!

Love, The East Fam

Music Credit to Josh Garrels (our favorite!) - https://www.joshgarrels.com/

About the East Fam...

At 28 years old, American gymnast Shawn Johnson has accomplished a lifetime of achievements that include Olympic Medals, a New York Times best-selling book, several businesses, a career in broadcast, and a mirror ball trophy after winning Dancing With The Stars. Shawn married Andrew East, with whom she has documented their life on their shared Youtube channel which has over 110 million views and a podcast which has climbed to #2 on the overall charts. Andrew East is an NFL athlete who most recently played with the Washington Football Team. His experience in the media space has led to coaching and consultation on behalf of Google for Fortune 500 companies for how to create engaging content. Andrew and Shawn recently welcomed their first child in October 2019 and are excited to announce their third pregnancy in this video!
